citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 1:00 pm on 01-Feb-
2023.
The inspector arrived at the facility and knocked on the door of the garage attached to the house. The inspector sent the
licensee a text message and called and left a message. The licensee replied and stated that he was not available for the
inspection. The inspector then left the facility.
End Section

narrative:
2.126(b) 
   
Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries. 
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 1:00 pm on 01-Feb-
2023.   
 
The inspector arrived at the facility and knocked on the door of the garage attached to the house.  The inspector sent the 
licensee a text message and called and left a message.  The licensee replied and stated that he was not available for the 
inspection.   The inspector then left the facility. 
 
 
 
End Section
